title: HotAndMean - Abigail Mac, Jessa Rhodes (The Ballad of Johnny Nat
description:
HotAndMean - Abigail Mac, Jessa Rhodes (The Ballad of Johnny Nathan Part 1 / Brazzers) 720p NEW April 07, 2016 

As the 1950s become the 1960s, washed up doo-wop singer Johnny Nathan finds himself without an audience, his musical relevance fading faster than his dignity. As a depressed Johnny contemplates leaving the music biz, he is approached by two former fans, Abigail Mac & Jessa Rhodes dressed in the height of flower power fashion. Abigail and Jessa drag Johnny to a hippie love in, where they blow his mind by dosing him with LSD and showing him just how dirty free love can be.
